text: Josef Milnarik (2 August 1903 - 30 November 1969) was an Austrian footballer. He played for Wiener Amateur SV and in one match for the Austria national football team in 1924. ==References== Category:1903 births Category:1969 deaths Category:Austrian footballers Category:Players of the Austrian national football team Category:Austrian football forwards Category:Austrian football champions
